metadata.name: The Triangle - Blazing Hope
metadata.description:
Kulasai Dussehra Festival - One of the most powerful grand festival in Tamilnadu.

Even after two full days of working from early morning until late at night, I was not happy with my captures.
But I didn't give up and continued to wait there until dark, when all the other photographers had left. I was the only one remaining waiting for the one of a kind shot, and at that very moment, I managed to get this frame. I feel fortunate to have this frame because this is my most memorable movement.


Artist : satzhema

Collection: Rituals

Edition: 1/1
